# Never commit real LP statements — only synthetic fixtures and PUBLIC
# illustrative documents (KPMG, CohnReznick, ILPA guidance). Defensive
# naming-pattern guards below catch the common slips. See
# examples/real_world/README.md for the full provenance rule.
examples/real/
examples/private/
examples/internal/
*.real.pdf
*.private.pdf
*.confidential.pdf
*.lp.pdf
examples/real_world/private_*
examples/real_world/lp_*
examples/real_world/confidential_*
examples/real_world/internal_*
